===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[bent|Bent]] to the point of coming apart, but not necessarily in separate pieces.
#: ''My arm is '''broken'''''
# Not [[working]] properly.
#: ''I think my shaver is '''broken'''.''
# Completely [[defeated]] and [[dispirited]].
#: ''The bankruptcy and divorce, together with the death of his son, left him completely '''broken'''.''
# {{context|software|colloquial}} [[badly|Badly]] [[designed]] or [[implemented]].
#: ''This is the most '''broken''' application I've seen in a long time.''
# {{sports}} A single [[tactic]] or [[option]] which is powerful enough to be considered [[overpowered]].
